HEADWORD: Unguled
<hw>Un"guled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>ungula</ets>
a claw.]</ety> <fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>Hoofed, or bearing hoofs; -- used
only when these are of a tincture different from the body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

